{"tid":691238,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛情][演藝][可能有甜]我係個配樂師，女朋友係舞台劇演員","createTime":"2018-06-05T14:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T08:14:57.000Z","uid":108844,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"644439d2ce2856fcb7012f5b1e1ecd3731371668","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係龜仔。之前只係喺創意台出過改詞post，最近想試下寫下故<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時未知會有幾長<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就一定唔會長到出書咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係想當係一個小劇場咁寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文筆唔好希望大家多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會勤力出文架！<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Another summer day<br />\nHas come and gone away<br />\nIn Paris and Rome<br />\nBut I wanna go home&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lbSOLBMUvIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlbSOLBMUvIE&d=mbGP7JXlvFSBBMzyTBH6yLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=c631a543\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lbSOLBMUvIE</a><br />\n<br />\n柔和嘅音樂緩緩響起，伴隨著電話嘅震動。哩首係Michael Bubl&eacute;嘅Home，亦係我嘅鬧鐘鈴聲。<br />\n<br />\n「呵哈～～～唔！」俾自己個口臭親。<br />\n<br />\n一打開電話，無數個whatsapp同未接來電不斷彈出......<br />\n<br />\n「Eric！快啲聽電話啦！」<br />\n<br />\n「你喺邊啊！」<br />\n<br />\n「Emily八點就on show喇！一陣遲咗冇得入場你唔好喊啊！」<br />\n<br />\n望一望個時間，依家已經七點！屋企去大會堂雖然唔係遠，但係我同Emily已經有一年冇見，我都想執靚仔少少自己先出門口。<br />\n<br />\n「SHIT！！！」<br />\n<br />\n我叫方文軒，今年22歲，係個配樂師。而Emily，係一個演員，亦係我嘅前度。<br />\n<br />\n我地喺三年前嘅一個舞台劇入面認識......<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n－三年前－<br />\n<br />\n「聽導演講上次開會大家都好滿意你寫嘅曲喎！尤其係嗰段鋼琴solo，簡直係扣人心弦啊！」<br />\n<br />\n「你飯鐘就有得扣！今日佢叫埋我嚟Run through，分分鐘又有嘢想我改啊！」<br />\n<br />\n副導演同我一邊行入場館一邊講。<br />\n<br />\n「Shhhhh......你地咁遲架！輝哥嗌咗開始喇！Eric你快啲過去啦，佢一路問你喺邊。」<br />\n<br />\n輝哥一係個非常有要求嘅導演同監製，對每一個細節都一絲不苟。今次係我接觸配樂以嚟第二次接到舞台劇音樂創作嘅工作，而第一次亦係同輝哥合作，當時我就俾佢不斷要求執啲編曲搞到冇覺好瞓。<br />\n<br />\n我吞一吞口水，放輕腳步行過去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   輝哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「輝哥早晨！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「早啊文軒！唔好意思早咗開始，食咗早餐未？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「唔緊要，食咗喇我。係呢，今日叫埋我嚟係咪啲歌有咩要執？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「唔係唔係！啲歌寫得好好，我都好滿意。但就係有啲位演員演嘅時候投入唔到音樂。所以想你俾啲意見。」<br />\n<br />\n哩個時候，音樂開始響起。哩一幕係女主角嘅內心獨白，背景音樂正是我寫嘅扣人飯鐘鋼琴曲。"},{"pid":"1129b2df68278a3832fc876f723e507e80acaf49","tid":691238,"uid":4210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"舞台劇演員留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbea76f39620997a5fcd6bc6f9ac16bf593bd45e","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"女主角留住一抹長髮，著住白色長裙，神情困惑地慢慢行到舞台中心。而喺觀眾席嘅我，完全俾佢嘅氣質所吸引住。佢望落好細個，我估可能得16,7歲。動作神態仍然成個細路女咁。<br />\n<br />\n「我應該知？我真係唔知呀！我好亂呀！佢的確為我改變咗好多，但我真係唔敢再信佢呀！我&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「等等！」<br />\n<br />\n女主角演到一半，突然被輝哥叫停。<br />\n<br />\n「阿女，你要記返起上次提過你嘅嘢。語氣要再誇張啲。」<br />\n<br />\n「但係個節奏仲係好難掌握啊&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n哩個時候，輝哥望一望我，再望返女主角。<br />\n<br />\n「阿女，哩位係我地今次嘅音樂總監文軒。我今日專誠叫埋佢嚟俾意見，你地認識下先啦。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「哦&hellip;知道。」<br />\n「Hello&hellip;叫我Eric得喇。」<br />\n<br />\nEmily：「He&hellip;Hello&hellip;我&hellip;我叫Emily啊&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\nEmily口疾疾咁，表情由好奇變成怕醜&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n原來佢叫Emily&hellip;...我地四目交投，莫名嘅緊張感越來越強烈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「um...其實首曲個mood主要係承接返上一段男主角向你告白&hellip;&hellip;」我講咗兩分幾鐘，Emily都好專心咁聽。但始終都帶住唔係好明嘅眼神&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「可能因為我未錄音，首曲仲係midi聲，令你投入唔到。或者我彈一次你跟住做。」<br />\n<br />\nEmily點點頭。我行去台邊嘅鋼琴前坐低。導演示意action，我就開始彈奏&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n鋼琴曲參考：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T-AkPwzL5Us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT-AkPwzL5Us&d=mbGP7JXlvFSBBMzyTBH6yLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=a45fbf5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T-AkPwzL5Us</a><br />\n<br />\n「我應該知？我真係唔知呀！我好亂呀！佢的確為我改變咗好多，但我真係唔敢再信佢呀！我應該點做&hellip;冇錯我係仲好愛佢，但係&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n有時候感覺就係咁微妙。喺哩一瞬間，我感覺我同Emily嘅情感連結埋一齊。佢每一個動作同我每一個音節都配合得天衣無縫，甚至演到雙眼通紅，完全表現到嗰種思緒混亂嘅不安。<br />\n<br />\n「Cut！非常好！就係要哩種感覺！阿女，keep住呀！」<br />\n<br />\n「知道！」Emily好開心咁望住我甜笑，好似小朋友比老師讚完想分享比人知咁。而我亦都微笑同還以一個手指公比佢，當然我個心都就嚟跳埋出嚟。"},{"pid":"2f835482f8abe09babf4f6fe617efc695c36df95","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1129b2df68278a3832fc876f723e507e80acaf49","tid":691238,"uid":4210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"舞台劇演員留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我做過一次之後覺得都係做返幕後算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f753e10837e0cce545cd44b1af5563fd1dbc25a","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a4549fabeaffecf9327a12a5ec36a4ed6c9f9a","tid":691238,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9457e7bcc1ef3e2a95650c3d5edcf31f595741","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37a4549fabeaffecf9327a12a5ec36a4ed6c9f9a","tid":691238,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"雪人bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f4988d1975ab7628712bd66afcfe6bdbbb6818","tid":691238,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9457e7bcc1ef3e2a95650c3d5edcf31f595741","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37a4549fabeaffecf9327a12a5ec36a4ed6c9f9a","tid":691238,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"雪人bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b04ae809c45aafbffb067365707cc90d2eacab","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"出多一小篇就訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n－[現在]前往大會堂嘅途中－<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;May be surrounded by<br />\nA million people I<br />\nStill feel all alone<br />\nJust wanna go home<br />\nOh, I miss you, you know&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我坐喺巴士上層車頭，耳機內嘅音樂伴隨住窗外雨水拍打嘅聲音。<br />\n<br />\n葵青劇院 &mdash;&mdash; 一個我同Emily一齊奮鬥過嘅地方。由於輝哥所屬嘅劇團資源唔少，加上喺葵青區，所以好自然地每次演出都係租用哩度。<br />\n<br />\n望住車外嘅環境，葵芳已經同之前好唔同。新裝修嘅新都會廣場，多咗個休憩花園。仲開咗間無印。可能因為咁，就算係雨天，人流都唔少。<br />\n<br />\n由於學業關係，同Emily分手後我都冇再接輝哥嘅工作。加上大學離葵青區比較遠，每日返學放學都直接返屋企，星期六日就返下兼職，所以我已經有一年冇去過葵芳。<br />\n<br />\n以前同Emily成日嚟哩度拍拖。一嚟方便去排劇，二嚟多嘢食。<br />\n<br />\n夏天嘅時候葵芳特別熱，所以我地都會盡快行入商場。真係好佩服大熱天時仲喺馬路旁邊炒栗子嘅姨姨。<br />\n<br />\n同好多女仔一樣，Emily好中意行葵涌廣場。因為學生時期冇錢，暑假要排劇又冇時間返part time。所以葵廣平價又靚嘅衫佢就最中意。<br />\n<br />\n而隔離新都會廣場我地都會行，但真係純粹得個行字。當係周圍散下步又有冷氣涼。反正同Emily一齊，去邊根本唔重要。<br />\n<br />\n「Emily咁鍾意花，新都會翻新成咁佢一定開心死啦～」我心諗。"},{"pid":"5a86b56d82c72eecb6498b5a52fb5eec78517cd3","tid":691238,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6bf3c10e0303d7cb4031713b4deec5b6a34d562","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5463b92e5506d5a6ba3af9c88b17bdf12129a575","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"－三年前again－<br />\n<br />\n第一次見面之後，我同Emily一路有keep contact。可能雙方都知道對方鍾意自己，所以我地好快就一齊咗。有時候排完劇，我地都會去附近嘅空地度拍拖，貪夠靜可以坐低談心。<br />\n<br />\n「我夢想係有朝一日，可以開屬於自己嘅作品展。台下坐滿觀眾，欣賞住我將自己寫過嘅歌一首一首咁演奏。」<br />\n<br />\n「咁我要坐第一排！」<br />\n<br />\n「唔得，我要你坐喺台上面！哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n「我先唔要！哼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「咁你呢？你嘅夢想係點架？」<br />\n<br />\n「我啊......其實我只要可以一直做演員就已經好滿足喇。無論台下有冇人睇我都會一直做！因為只要我一企上台演戲，就會覺得好實在。所以，我已經實現緊我嘅夢想架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n好多人包括我，都視夢想為地平線。覺得夢想遙不可及，好難甚至冇可能實現。於是有放棄嘅人，亦有停滯不前嘅人。<br />\n而Emily，佢清楚自己一早就處於地平線上，無論自己行到幾遠，佢每一步經過嘅都係地平線。<br />\n哩個女仔真係好特別，我越來越欣賞同鍾意佢。<br />\n<br />\n「以後每套劇我都送一束花比你好冇～」<br />\n<br />\n「嘻嘻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁如果再加埋以後每套劇都係你做音樂總監就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「傻妹～」"},{"pid":"8b9e82d6ccc56d80a554948f9011a1eefe37c103","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc2e99d9de652cd7a46b8d2b16d1364e509e939","tid":691238,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"睇緊"},{"pid":"1cc0b3d7bcfe60c310c88c19bf89204ab6d2b28b","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"第一小篇似四月是你的謊言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addf9c4cc2de9720e66fbed9a53e60d1b0fe732c","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc2e99d9de652cd7a46b8d2b16d1364e509e939","tid":691238,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"睇緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33984eb988ce4f8051f036b08b6a9987afe83a71","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc0b3d7bcfe60c310c88c19bf89204ab6d2b28b","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"第一小篇似四月是你的謊言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"其實有啲驚用插敘喺唔同時間點跳嚟跳去會令人睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea57