白色嘅教堂入面。所有親友都嚟齊祝福你地。你西裝畢挺，著住婚紗嘅佢，一心期待被你揭開頭紗擁吻。你地喺牧師嘅見證下讀出誓詞。最後一句我願意，你地交換戒指，終於成為合法夫妻，同偕白首。<br />\n<br />\n其實你地都冇信教，只係喺裝潢優雅嘅教堂入面結婚好似係自細被耳濡目染所得來嘅概念，係浪漫嘅指標。你覺得佢都一定中意。<br />\n<br />\n你甚至有諗過將來你地嘅仔女叫咩名。<br />\n<br />\n「嗱！男嘅就叫方文山，女嘅就將你嘅英文名直譯中文。叫方美麗啦！」<br />\n「咁核突！唔得啊！」<br />\n「但方美麗唔可以嫁比姓吳嘅男仔，因為如果跟老公姓就會變成吳方美麗喇！哈哈哈哈！」<br />\n「你要唔要睇下精神科！同埋邊個話同你生喎！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憧憬本質係正面而幸福，但成長往往唔及現實變化嘅速度之快。而哩個時候，憧憬就成為你心中最錐心嘅痛。"},{"pid":"25bff9912333ab7d369f44cf08bf23cc0d82ab4a","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cba621d67e11fbe700ca525eea4bad075c96599","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a44aa90187853f05b2b8b60551a4e8357b81dd","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baed105d3589bb2f71e95782afdac71104c5891d","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢係音樂，你係演藝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"都會著筆寫下男主角喺音樂方面嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:19:46.000Z","msg":"我會注意樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04f50ebfe8680174b13ca8bf3e574b955c8a67f","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25bff9912333ab7d369f44cf08bf23cc0d82ab4a","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cba621d67e11fbe700ca525eea4bad075c96599","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a44aa90187853f05b2b8b60551a4e8357b81dd","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like