/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> why so短嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"哩篇同劇情擺埋一齊po好似冇咁有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db391a97bfa40ab61197a0ebbc897bf786df7852","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"你肯出未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你禁耐都仲未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c706653743cc670bd0b24ce312b232eb06282992","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db391a97bfa40ab61197a0ebbc897bf786df7852","tid":691238,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"你肯出未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等你禁耐都仲未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"就出喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c0b754b13d9b8b44fb96a9b3308352b7f38924","tid":691238,"uid":129410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:57:14.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f56e31f6ad7eb16f952344e9b33ccf78bcee7501","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n「方文軒？」<br />\n<br />\n落車後，一把女聲傳入耳內，將我由回憶拉返現實。<br />\n我回頭一望，原來係Emily嘅好朋友阿晴。<br />\n<br />\n阿晴係個好活潑嘅女仔，但同時又好八卦。<br />\n<br />\n「你都係嚟睇Emily套劇架？」阿晴帶住有花生食嘅表情問我。<br />\n<br />\n「呃&hellip;係啊。但你可唔可以唔好話俾佢知？我唔想影響佢心情......」<br />\n<br />\n「唉，明嘅。嗰時你激到佢咁嬲，都唔知佢再見返你會點諗。」<br />\n<br />\n傾咗兩句，阿晴就突然話要搵埋另一個朋友，同我分別。<br />\n<br />\n我見仲有20分鐘先入場，就去starbucks買咗杯咖啡醒醒神。前一晚通宵錄音令我朝早11點先返到屋企訓覺，所以先差啲唔知醒......<br />\n<br />\n有人話：咖啡先苦後甘。飲嘅人如果抱住享受放鬆嘅心，咖啡就會回甘。相反，如果只係用嚟提神續命，咁咖啡就只有苦。<br />\n<br />\n甘味需要時間醞釀。做人亦然，必需要經歷低谷困境，捱過後先會迎來雨後甘露。而哩個過程，並唔係命運嘅安排，而係成長嘅必經階段。<br />\n<br />\n不幸嘅係，喺感情世界裡面，一旦對方感受到你嘅苦澀，好多時都等唔到回甘嘅來臨，雙方就會因為爭吵而分開。就好似飲咖啡咁，起初一定會嫌棄佢嘅苦味，繼而放棄續杯嘅念頭。到你終於頓悟成長，解脫心中曾經因為執著而種下嘅迷思嗰時，對方已經喺你嘅世界入面消失得無影無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n「一杯double espresso啊唔該。」<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n－回憶－<br />\n<br />\n「唔......好苦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！乜你飲埋啲咁嘅野架！你一陣唔好錫我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」Emily飲咗一啖double espresso，面容即刻扭曲晒。<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈！細蚊仔唔識飲espresso架喇！你都係飲返焦糖咖啡啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「咩細蚊仔啊！我拎咗成人身份證！大個女架喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈！邊個琴晚訓覺仲啜緊手指！」<br />\n<br />\n「咩喎！明明係你擺我隻手去我咀邊！」<br />\n<br />\n「但你即刻就拎嚟啜喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「哼！你就細蚊仔！唔知邊個第一次見我嗰陣紅都面哂呢～好似小朋友未見過靚女咁～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「車！嗰陣你直情怕醜到講嘢一舊舊添啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n「邊...邊有喎！！」<br />\n<br />\n「嗱嗱嗱！又疾喇！」<br />\n<br />\n「哼！唔同你玩！」<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"2bcb60611f4c0ec4032991f6bac7358c4d1ae375","tid":691238,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70069812a99b2506d06e0b72a2eaac27552fad1","tid":691238,"uid":129410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1